---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="About"
  description="About Ibrahim Rafi — software engineer in Dhaka, Bangladesh. Arch Linux user, self-hoster, security-minded builder."
>
  <h1 class="page-title">About</h1>

  <div class="bio">
    <p>
      I'm Ibrahim — a software engineer in Dhaka, Bangladesh. I studied
      electronics and communication engineering at Khulna University, drifted
      from circuits to code, and never looked back.
    </p>
    <p>
      I run Arch Linux (yes, by the way). I self-host things that absolutely do
      not need self-hosting — a music player, a package mirror, file servers —
      because owning your own infrastructure is its own reward. When something
      is closed, locked, or "not supported on your device", that's usually where
      my next project comes from.
    </p>
    <p>
      What I keep coming back to is what's beneath the surface — how things
      really work, where the trust assumptions are, what happens when you poke
      at them. It started with small
      <a href="/steg">steganography experiments</a> in university and turned into
      a security-minded way of building software.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="contact">
    <h2 class="label">Find me</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="mailto:me@ibrahimrafi.me">me@ibrahimrafi.me</a></li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://github.com/rafiibrahim8">github.com/rafiibrahim8</a>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .bio {
    max-width: 680px;
    font-size: 17.5px;
  }

  .bio p {
    margin-bottom: 1.2em;
  }

  .bio a {
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--accent);
  }

  .contact {
    margin-top: 56px;
  }

  .contact h2 {
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .contact ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .contact li {
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .contact a {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--ink);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--accent);
  }

  .contact a:hover {
    color: var(--accent);
  }
</style>
